metadata.name: Bored Panda Yatch Gang #1
metadata.description: The Bored Panda Yatch Gang is a collection of 1010 unique Panda NFTs unique digital collectibles living on the Ethereum blockchain. Your Bored Panda doubles as your Yacht Gang membership card, and grants access to members-only benefits, the first of which is access to THE PANDA'S ROOM, a collaborative graffiti Panda Paw. Future areas and perks can be unlocked by the community through roadmap activation.
